1. Introduction

This Privacy Policy describes how BettaBase Management (“the App”), developed by ÁlvaroFr for APB (“we”, “us”, or “our”), collects, uses, and protects user information.

By using the App, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this Privacy Policy.

2. Information We Collect

To use BettaBase Management, users are required to create an account. During registration and normal use of the App, we may collect the following information:

Account information (such as email address and login credentials)

App usage data related to features and functionality

Purchase and subscription status (to determine access to Pro features)

We do not collect sensitive personal data such as precise location, contacts, photos, or payment card details.

3. Payments and Pro Features

The App offers optional paid features (“Pro version”) that can be unlocked through in-app purchases.

All payments are processed securely by Google Play Billing. We do not collect, store, or process payment card or financial information. We only receive confirmation of purchase and subscription status from Google to enable Pro features.

4. Use of Information

The information collected is used solely to:

Create and manage user accounts

Enable core and Pro app functionality

Verify purchase status and access rights

Improve app performance and reliability

Provide user support when requested

5. Third-Party Services

The App uses third-party services that may collect information used to identify you. These services operate under their own privacy policies:

Google Play Services
https://policies.google.com/privacy

6. Data Security

We take reasonable measures to protect user information and prevent unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure. However, no method of electronic transmission or storage is completely secure, and absolute security cannot be guaranteed.

7. Data Retention

User data is retained only for as long as necessary to provide the App’s functionality or to comply with legal obligations. Users may request account deletion by contacting us.

8. Children’s Privacy

BettaBase Management is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If such information is discovered, it will be deleted promptly.

9. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and the “Last updated” date will be revised accordingly.

10. Contact Us

If you have any questions or requests regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

Email: bettafishapk@gmail.com
